From f0559cc05b70b7e8353f5be3d8dcd22832ba5d15 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Jithender Kondam <jreddy@marvell.com>
Date: Tue, 3 Feb 2026 07:41:00 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] [QoS] Enhance SONiC CLI for WRED profile creation and
 deletion support

Enhance SONiC CLI commands `ecnconfig` and `config ecn` to allow runtime creation and deletion of WRED profiles, addressing the limitation where profiles could only be modified if they already existed.

- Added `-create` option for profile creation
- Added `-delete` option for profile deletion
- Added `-ecn` option for ECN mode configuration
- Added `-green-enable`, `-yellow-enable`, `-red-enable` options

```bash
config ecn -create -profile PROFILE_NAME \
  -gmin 1048576 -gmax 2097152 -gdrop 5 \
  -ymin 1048576 -ymax 2097152 -ydrop 5 \
  -rmin 1048576 -rmax 2097152 -rdrop 5 \
  -ecn ecn_all -green-enable -v
```

```bash
config ecn -delete -profile PROFILE_NAME -v
```

```bash
config ecn -profile PROFILE_NAME -rmax 3145728 -rdrop 10 -v
```

Signed-off-by: Jithender Kondam <jreddy@marvell.com>
